fields.name: MigrationState
fields.description: State in which Standard to Premium Migration is, possible values : Unknown, Reverting, Completing, Initiating, Syncing, Active

fields.name: PendingReplicationOperationsCount
fields.description: Number of entities pending to be replicated.

fields.name: PostMigrationName
fields.description: Name to access Standard Namespace after migration

fields.name: TargetNamespace
fields.description: Existing premium Namespace ARM Id name which has no entities, will be used for migration
